title: @OspreyWTEN Wraps Up Day Two of South Carolina Fall Classic
text: and Hemmerich were tripped up 6-2 by Ellie Zogg and Ingrid Gamarra Martins. Paige Cline and Rachel Rohrabacher defeated Valdez and Intert 6-1. Calderon and Fluhrer fell 6-0 to Hadley Berg and Brigit Folland. UNF finishes competition at the South Carolina Fall Classic on Sunday with just singles matches against South Carolina at 9 a.m. South Carolina Fall Classic Day Two Results Singles
